{"word":"Levites","slug":"levites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Levites</b> The descendants of Levi.<br/> Set apart as ministers of religion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=54'>Num 1:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=16'>Num 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=9'>Num 16:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=62'>Num 26:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=8'>Deu 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=2'>1Ch 15:2</a><br/> Substituted in the place of the firstborn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=12'>Num 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=45'>Num 3:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=14'>Num 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=18'>Num 8:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=6'>Num 18:6</a><br/> Religious zeal of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=28'>Exo 32:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=10'>Deu 33:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=2&verse=5'>Mal 2:5</a><br/> Consecration of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=21'>Num 8:21</a><br/> Sedition among, led by Korah, Dathan, Abiram, and On, on account of jealousy toward Moses and Aaron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16'>Num 16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=20'>Num 4:20</a><br/> Three divisions of:<br/> - Each having the name of one of its progenitors, Gershon, Kohath, and Merari<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=17'>Num 3:17</a> <br/> - Gershonites:<br/> b Gershonites and their duties<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=26'>Num 3:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=26'>Num 4:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=17'>Num 10:17</a><br/> b Ruling chief over the Gershonites was the second son of the ruling high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=28'>Num 4:28</a><br/> - Kohathites:<br/> b the families of the Amramites, Izeharites, Hebronites, Uzzielites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=27'>Num 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=20'>Num 4:20</a><br/> b of the Amramites, Aaron and his family were set apart as priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=1'>Exo 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=38'>Num 3:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=13'>Num 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=14'>Num 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=1'>Num 18:1</a><br/> b the remaining families appointed to take charge of the ark, table, candlestick, altars, and vessels of the sanctuary, the hangings, and all the service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=32'>Num 3:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=15'>Num 4:15</a><br/> b the chief over the Kohathites was the oldest son of the ruling high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=32'>Num 3:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=20'>1Ch 9:20</a><br/> - Merarites:<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=20'>Num 3:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=37'>Num 3:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=33'>Num 4:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=8'>Num 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=17'>Num 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=19'>1Ch 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=30'>1Ch 6:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=23'>1Ch 23:23</a><br/> b the chief over the Merarites was the second son of the ruling high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=33'>Num 4:33</a><br/> Place of, in camp and march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=53'>Num 1:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=17'>Num 2:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=35'>Num 3:35</a><br/> Cities assigned to, in the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21'>Jos 21</a><br/> Lodged in the chambers of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=27'>1Ch 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=33'>1Ch 9:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=40&verse=44'>Eze 40:44</a><br/> Resided also in villages outside of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=29'>Neh 12:29</a><br/> Age of:<br/> - When inducted into office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=3'>Num 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=30'>Num 4:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=47'>Num 4:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=26'>Num 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=3'>1Ch 23:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=24'>1Ch 23:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=27'>1Ch 23:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=8'>Ezr 3:8</a> <br/> - When retired from office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=3'>Num 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=47'>Num 4:47</a> <br/> Functions of:<br/> - Had charge of the tabernacle in camp and on the march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=53'>Num 1:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=9'>Num 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=37'>Num 3:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=15'>Num 4:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=49'>Num 4:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=19'>Num 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=6'>Num 18:6</a> <br/> - Had charge of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=29'>1Ch 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=32'>1Ch 23:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=34'>Ezr 8:34</a> <br/> - Bore the ark of the covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=8'>Deu 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=2'>1Ch 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=27'>1Ch 15:27</a> <br/> - Ministered before the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=4'>1Ch 16:4</a> <br/> - Custodians and administrators of the tithes and other offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=29'>1Ch 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=28'>1Ch 26:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=8'>1Ch 29:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=5'>2Ch 24:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=11'>2Ch 24:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=19'>2Ch 31:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=9'>2Ch 34:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=30'>Ezr 8:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=33'>Ezr 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=44'>Neh 12:44</a> <br/> - Prepared the shewbread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=29'>1Ch 23:29</a> <br/> - Assisted the priests in preparing the sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=36'>2Ch 29:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=18'>2Ch 35:18</a> <br/> - Killed the Passover for the children of the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=21'>Ezr 6:21</a> <br/> - Teachers of the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=10'>Deu 33:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=9'>2Ch 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=22'>2Ch 30:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=3'>2Ch 35:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=13'>Neh 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=2&verse=7'>Mal 2:7</a> <br/> - Were judges<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=9'>Deu 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=4'>1Ch 23:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=29'>1Ch 26:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=11'>2Ch 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=16'>Neh 11:16</a><br/><a href='S:Judge'>Judge</a><br/> b Reference book of Judges<br/> <a href='B:'></a><br/> - Were scribes of the sacred books<br/> <a href='S:Scribe'>Scribe</a> <br/> - Pronounced the blessings of the law in the responsive service at Mount Gerizim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=12'>Deu 27:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=33'>Jos 8:33</a> <br/> - Were porters of the doors<br/> <a href='S:Porters'>Porters</a> <br/> - Were overseers in building and the repairs of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=4'>1Ch 23:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=9'>Ezr 3:9</a> <br/> - Were musicians of the temple service<br/> <a href='S:Music'>Music</a> <br/> - Supervised weights and measures<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=29'>1Ch 23:29</a> <br/> List of those who returned from captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=63'>Ezr 2:63</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=7'>Ezr 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=20'>Ezr 8:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=73'>Neh 7:73</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12'>Neh 12</a><br/> Sealed the covenant with Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=28'>Neh 10:28</a><br/> Emoluments (compensations) of:<br/> - In lieu of landed inheritance, forty-eight cities with suburbs were assigned to them<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=8'>Num 35:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=24'>Num 18:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=62'>Num 26:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=9'>Deu 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=12'>Deu 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=19'>Deu 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=29'>Deu 14:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=8'>Deu 18:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=14'>Jos 13:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=3'>Jos 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=7'>Jos 18:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=81'>1Ch 6:81</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=2'>1Ch 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=2'>2Ch 23:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=34&verse=5'>Eze 34:5</a> <br/> - Assigned to, by families<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=40'>Jos 21:40</a> <br/> - Suburbs of their cities were inalienable for debt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=34'>Lev 25:34</a> <br/> - Tithes and other offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=24'>Num 18:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=32'>Num 18:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=8'>Deu 18:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=26&verse=13'>Deu 26:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=14'>Jos 13:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=39'>Neh 10:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=44'>Neh 12:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=47'>Neh 12:47</a> <br/> - First fruits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=44'>Neh 12:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=47'>Neh 12:47</a> <br/> Spoils of war, including captives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=30'>Num 31:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=47'>Num 31:47</a><br/><a href='S:Tithes'>Tithes</a><br/> - Tithes withheld from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=13'>Neh 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=10'>Mal 3:10</a> <br/> - Pensioned<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=18'>2Ch 31:18</a> <br/> - Owned lands<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=8'>Deu 18:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=26'>1Ki 2:26</a> <br/> - Land allotted to, by Ezekiel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=14'>Eze 48:14</a> <br/> Enrollment of, at Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=49'>Num 1:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=33'>Num 2:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=39'>Num 3:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=3'>Num 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=62'>Num 26:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=5'>1Ch 23:5</a><br/> Degraded from the Levitical office by Jeroboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=17'>2Ch 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=11'>2Ch 13:11</a><br/> Loyal to the ruler<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=11'>2Ki 11:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=7'>2Ch 23:7</a><br/> Intermarry with Canaanites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=2'>Ezr 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=24'>Ezr 10:24</a><br/> Exempt from enrollment for military duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=54'>Num 1:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=26'>1Ch 12:26</a><br/> Subordinate to the sons of Aaron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=9'>Num 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=19'>Num 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=6'>Num 18:6</a><br/> Prophecies concerning:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=33&verse=18'>Jer 33:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=14'>Eze 44:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=3'>Mal 3:3</a> <br/> - Of their repentance of the crucifixion of the Messiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=12&verse=13'>Zec 12:13</a> <br/> - John's vision concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=7&verse=7'>Rev 7:7</a> "}]}